status_message:
Recent Guest Reviews:

"This place is charming! The interior is beautifully decorated, with extra touches all around. The outside is peaceful and quiet, with trails to walk and enjoy the outdoors, or a screened in porch to relax and reflect." --Tiara

"If you're looking for something local to Kansas City, yet feel so far away hidden in nature with the beautiful ambience this is your place. It was a super quiet and peaceful place that enabled us to connect and embrace everything around! It was super cozy, very spacious and inviting for all. We will definitely make this one of our must visit again places for a longer period next time." - Michelle

"The retreat is definitely worth a visit! So much so that we already want to come back. You can't beat the coziness of the guesthouse and treehouse. Stan and Denise are lovely and put so many wonderful touches into everything. I need more than five stars to rate it!" - -Megan

https://www.facebook.com/bosseconstructionservices/

Darrel and Sue Bosse,  from Bosse Construction, made this cedar table and several other beautiful pieces! Thank you:) These two are amazing professionals ! A coating of poly this morning - look at this wood beauty!! Getting furniture ready for treehouse!

Following a few months of recovery from an unfortunate accident, Graham's Cove Treehouse is under construction! This will be a rustic treehouse retreat space. Building plans: Nelson's Treehouse Masters.
It is a beautiful snow day here in 'The Valley'! We are open for guests - booking 3 months out. For booking dates further out, please contact us directly.

status_message: Today's much needed rain sent us working inside the retreat house's second wing.  (Open for booking October 2017!) The history of this priest's wing was an artist and writer's area. We plan to create a space that will continue to inspire creativity. The back hallway seemed to be a place to start rehab since a bucket of paint spilled on the carpet when doing a 'quick' paint job;/ Ho-hum!!!

The tranquil sound of the Koi pond waterfall along with the outdoor sounds of summer can be heard in 'The Valley'! Come to relax and leave refreshed! #treehouse #fortleavenworth #stationedatfortleavenworth #hiking #nature
Escape to a treehouse and retreat house in the quiet peaceful wilderness 10 mi north of Leavenworth, Kansas! #Airbnb #treehouse  #fortleavenworth #hiking #nature #kansascity

..And so .... the journey begins for a more adventurous treehouse #2! Stay tuned! The boards will be sanded and edges routered for interior shiplap siding. Ahhh.... The smell of red cedar!! If you could design a treehouse, what would you plan?

status_message: The first treehouse at Hidden Valley Wilderness Retreat is open for guests! This bedroom treehouse is an extension of the original priest retreat suite. The retreat suite offers a full kitchen, master bedroom (king size bed) w bath, sunken living room and screened in patio overlooking the koi pond. July introduction promo $99 weeknight / $125 weekend for 2 people. $25/ per each addl person.

The private suite includes a full kitchen, large bedroom w sitting area, private bathroom, living room, screened in porch overlooking a koi pond and covered parking.
